1
00:00:00,880 --> 00:00:02,460
How should I put this?

2
00:00:02,460 --> 00:00:04,920
Working together like this...

3
00:00:04,920 --> 00:00:06,550
brings back so many feelings.

4
00:00:06,550 --> 00:00:08,380
What's that supposed to mean?

5
00:00:08,380 --> 00:00:10,640
And here I thought you were going to say
something romantic.

6
00:00:10,640 --> 00:00:13,260
What? I can't say things like that
at work.

7
00:00:13,560 --> 00:00:15,180
Oh, really?

8
00:00:15,600 --> 00:00:19,600
Then I'll expect to hear it
outside of work.

9
00:00:19,600 --> 00:00:21,650
Motomiya-san.

10
00:00:21,650 --> 00:00:23,110
Hey, stop playing with my ear.

11
00:00:23,110 --> 00:00:24,520
Hahaha.

12
00:00:24,520 --> 00:00:26,230
Excuse me.

13
00:00:27,400 --> 00:00:30,210
Makoto, I need a word with you.

14
00:00:30,660 --> 00:00:33,510
Oh, is it important?
Should I step out?

15
00:00:34,450 --> 00:00:37,700
Actually, yes. That would help.

16
00:00:38,200 --> 00:00:39,660
Here, take this.

17
00:00:39,660 --> 00:00:40,960
Do you know how to use it?

18
00:00:40,960 --> 00:00:42,670
Just dab it gently.

19
00:00:42,670 --> 00:00:44,880
I know. Thanks.

20
00:00:45,250 --> 00:00:46,090
Thank you.

21
00:00:46,090 --> 00:00:47,090
No problem.

22
00:00:50,800 --> 00:00:52,550
Um, Shiono-san...

23
00:00:52,550 --> 00:00:53,930
You wanted to talk?

24
00:00:53,930 --> 00:00:55,970
Did I do something wrong?

25
00:00:57,350 --> 00:00:59,310
Makoto...
